snippet: A booster rocket successfully launched an unmanned cargo ship to the station, whose crew is anxiously awaiting it after the failures of two previous supply missions.
abstract: Russian booster rocket successfully launches unmanned supply ship to International Space Station, providing relief to astronauts awaiting supplies following two previous failed attempts.
lead_paragraph: A booster rocket successfully launched an unmanned cargo ship to the station, whose crew is anxiously awaiting it after the failures of two previous supply missions.

headline.main: Russian Supply Ship Is Launched to International Space Station
headline.print_headline: Russia Launches Supply Ship for International Space Station
